This is all of what I  use for vim

This repository contains 2 submodules so run
git submodule init
git submodule update

to get everything

or

git clone --recursive 

Note: to git rid of the funky mouse wheel scroll down behaviour
in the nerdtree view when using putty,
edit vim/bundle/nerdtree/plugin/NERD_tree.vim
comment out the line that maps <MiddleRelease> to the function
"handleMiddleMouse"

